  "body": "<img alt=\"22a-DSC_1296-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599888819815-LWTT6OHH67KJGKN8KREK/22a-DSC_1296-600x398.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"22b-DSC_1295-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599888819917-20HMOW3GXQM91WB6OLIA/22b-DSC_1295-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22c-DSC_1297-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599888820230-RQXW6JMC12L0O8X4MITA/22c-DSC_1297-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22d-DSC_1299-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599888820328-17CX0NY80EOVGZU7IV01/22d-DSC_1299-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22e-DSC_1303-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599888820689-BYWUUQBI8WA1L85LLX7C/22e-DSC_1303-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"22f-DSC_1304-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599888820754-B3TOZD9HL6S1BR1TKLJY/22f-DSC_1304-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/silhouette-cameo-machine/silhouette-cameo?aff=6cc2c70f\">Silhouette</a> got a lot of use this month. The <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1awBDfK\">digital cut files</a> are out of this world and so easy to use. </p><p>I could have easily made a dozen layouts with the <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/roundabout?aff=6cc2c70f\">Roundabout kits</a> from Studio Calico, but I was out of town for much of May. Actually, I spent every single weekend away from home. One of them was at Camp Calico, where I made <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/galleries/89994-hello-melbourne?aff=6cc2c70f\">this layout</a>. You can see all 8 of my projects in the gallery <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/creative-team-gallery/roundabout/scrapbook/amy-tan--2?aff=6cc2c70f\">here</a>.</p>"
